snippet.title: The Shadow SNES intro and level 1: Time Square
snippet.description:
Unreleased 1994 beat em'up game based on (veeeery underrated) movie of the same name. Collision detection could've been better. Or maybe it's just I suck at the game,
Graphics are nice and music is not that bad.
